
@startuml
skinparam linetype zigzag

class Customer {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -contactInfo: String
  -broker: Broker
  -policies: Set<Policy>
  -claims: Set<Claim>
}

class Broker {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -contactInfo: String
  -customers: Set<Customer>
  -policies: Set<Policy>
}

class Policy {
  -id: int
  -type: String
  -premium: double
  -duration: String
  -status: String
  -customer: Customer
  -contract: Contract
}

class Contract {
  -id: int
  -dateSigned: Date
  -terms: String
  -policy: Policy
  -customer: Customer
  -invoices: Set<Invoice>
}

class Invoice {
  -id: int
  -amount: double
  -dueDate: Date
  -paymentStatus: String
  -contract: Contract
}

class Claim {
  -id: int
  -dateSubmitted: Date
  -description: String
  -status: String
  -customer: Customer
  -cases: Set<ClaimCase>
  -compensation: Compensation
}

class ClaimCase {
  -id: int
  -type: String
  -description: String
  -status: String
  -claim: Claim
  -estimators: Set<Estimator>
  -reports: Set<EstimatorReport>
}

class Estimator {
  -id: int
  -name: String
  -expertiseArea: String
  -reports: Set<EstimatorReport>
}

class EstimatorReport {
  -id: int
  -dateSubmitted: Date
  -findings: String
  -approvalStatus: String
  -claimCase: ClaimCase
  -estimator: Estimator
}

class Compensation {
  -id: int
  -amount: double
  -datePaid: Date
  -claim: Claim
  -eligibleCosts: Map<String, Double>
}

Customer "1" -- "1" Broker : assigned to
Broker "1" -- "0..*" Customer : manages
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Policy : has
Broker "1" -- "0..*" Policy : handles
Policy "1" -- "1" Contract : associated with
Contract "1" -- "0..*" Invoice : generates
Customer "1" -- "0..*" Claim : files
Claim "1" -- "1" Compensation : results in
Claim "1" -- "0..*" ClaimCase : contains
ClaimCase "1" -- "0..*" Estimator : involves
Estimator "1" -- "0..*" EstimatorReport : submits
ClaimCase "1" -- "0..*" EstimatorReport : receives
@enduml

---

### ✅ Summary of Key Entities:
- **Customer**: Has a broker, can have multiple policies and claims.
- **Broker**: Manages customers and policies.
- **Policy**: Associated with a customer and a contract.
- **Contract**: Signed by customer and broker, includes invoices.
- **Invoice**: Generated from the contract.
- **Claim**: Filed by a customer, may have multiple claim cases.
- **ClaimCase**: A sub-case of a claim handled by estimators.
- **Estimator**: Handles claim cases and provides reports.
- **EstimatorReport**: Evaluates a claim case.
- **Compensation**: Paid to customer after claim approval.

---

